        <img alt="Water recycling systems around the building" class="inline-image edit-image-button" src="./media/water-recycling-graphic_comp-lr_orkt7kq.jpg" data-min-width-1401="./media/water-recycling-graphic_comp-mr_wtpmz4x.jpg" />
      
      <p class="caption">Water recycling systems around the building</p>
    
</aside>
